    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and bodywork to be roadworthy again. The engine struggles to start, the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping, and there are several fluid leaks that need addressing. Cosmetically, the exterior has extensive rust and paint peeling, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is being sold as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or as a source for parts.",
