    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to rigorous standards to ensure reliable performance and enduring structural integrity. Featuring a well-appointed cabin and a responsive drivetrain, it offers a refined driving experience suitable for the discerning professional. Every system has been thoroughly vetted to confirm its road-readiness, representing a premier opportunity for a buyer seeking a balance of luxury and dependable service.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready for its next adventure with you! Everything runs smooth, it looks great, and it\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six remains potent, featuring a responsive double-VANOS system and crisp individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential, ensuring classic rear-drive dynamics. This vehicle has received essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, preserving the structural rigidity and longevity of the chassis. The suspension retains its factory-spec composure with refreshed bushings, offering the communicative steering feedback synonymous with the M-division. A well-sorted driver's car that balances performance heritage with reliable mechanical upkeep.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained and reliable premium sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though closer inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been a strictly non-smoking environment. The leather upholstery remains supple, with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is in robust health; it has a complete service history, with a recent oil service and brake pad replacement performed just 1,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, effortless shifts. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next owner to drive with confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring consistent performance and a sophisticated driving experience. With a well-preserved exterior and a meticulously kept cabin, it represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking lasting value and dependable engineering.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road for its next big adventure! It runs like a charm and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable, comfy car that still looks great. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This driver-spec example is equipped with a 6-speed manual transmission and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), allowing for precise adjustment of the suspension's compression and rebound characteristics. The M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional mechanical grip, while the hydraulic steering rack offers the tactile feedback modern EPS systems lack. Crucially, the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014common S65 failure points\u2014have been addressed, ensuring the longevity of the valvetrain and bottom end. While the Alpine White finish shows minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the chassis remains rigid and the engine pulls strongly through the entire powerband. A purist\u2019s machine with all critical maintenance current.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
